#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&knetattach; is a wizard which makes it easier to integrate your network "
"resources with your &kde; Desktop."
msgstr ""
"&knetattach; je čarovnik, ki olajša povezovanje omrežnih virov z vašim "
"namizjem &kde;."

