#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &knetattach; wizard, affectionately and hereafter known as the Network "
"Folder Wizard, allows easy addition and integration of various network "
"folders with your &kde; desktop. Please report any problems or feature "
"requests for it to the &kde; bugs website."
msgstr ""
"Čarovnik &knetattach;, v nadaljevanju znan kot čarovnik za omrežne mape, "
"omogoča enostavno dodajanje in povezovanje različnih omrežnih map z vašim "
"namizjem &kde;. O morebitnih težavah ali zahtevah po funkcijah poročajte na "
"spletnem mestu &kde; hrošči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &knetattach;"
msgstr "Uporaba &knetattach;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you will see in the screenshot below, the Network Folder Wizard currently "
"allows you to add four types of network folders: WebDav, &FTP;, &Microsoft; "
"&Windows; (&Samba;) network drives and SSH. Additionally you can select a "
"recent connection for the list box."
msgstr ""
"Kot vidite na spodnji sliki zajetega zaslona, čarovnik za omrežne mape "
"trenutno omogoča dodajanje štirih vrst omrežnih map: WebDav, &FTP;, "
"&Microsoft; &Windows; (&Samba;) omrežni pogoni in SSH. Poleg tega lahko v "
"polju seznama izberete nedavno povezavo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &knetattach;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona za &knetattach;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:96 index.docbook:124 index.docbook:264 index.docbook:288
#: index.docbook:306 index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network Folder Wizard main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno čarovnika za omrežne mape"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding network folders"
msgstr "Dodajanje omrežnih map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Network folders show up in a special location of &konqueror; and &dolphin; "
"called a <emphasis>virtual folder</emphasis>. This virtual folder is "
"accessed by typing <userinput>remote:/</userinput> in the location bar or by "
"selecting <guilabel>Network</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel. You will then be able to see any folders which have been previously "
"added and you also will be able to use the wizard to add new ones."
msgstr ""
"Omrežne mape se prikažejo na posebnem mestu v programih &konqueror; in "
"&dolphin;, ki se imenuje <emphasis>virtualna mapa</emphasis>. Do te "
"navidezne mape dostopate tako, da v lokacijsko vrstico vnesete "
"<userinput>remote:/</userinput> ali izberete <guilabel>Omrežje</guilabel> na "
"plošči <guilabel>Kraji</guilabel>. Nato boste lahko videli vse mape, ki ste "
"jih že dodali, in lahko s čarovnikom dodate nove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "The virtual folder with the Network Folder wizard"
msgstr "Virtualna mapa s čarovnikom za omrežno mapo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Speaking of wizards, the Network Folder Wizard aims at being very easy to "
"use. After opening the wizard you must choose the type of network folder you "
"would like to access. When you move on to the next screen you will just need "
"to fill in the requested information. The final step is entering your "
"username and login password for the network share you've chosen to access."
msgstr ""
"Ko že govorimo o čarovnikih, je čarovnik za omrežne mape zelo enostaven za "
"uporabo. Po odprtju čarovnika morate izbrati vrsto omrežne mape, do katere "
"želite dostopati. Ko se premaknete na naslednji zaslon, morate samo "
"izpolniti zahtevane podatke. Zadnji korak je vnos uporabniškega imena in "
"prijavnega gesla za omrežni delež, do katerega ste se odločili dostopati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below is a list of the information needed by the wizard to create the "
"network folders. If an option is not available for a particular folder it "
"does not have to be entered. The &Samba; folders &eg; do not require a "
"<guilabel>Port</guilabel> entry."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je seznam informacij, ki jih čarovnik potrebuje za ustvarjanje "
"omrežnih map. Če možnost za določeno mapo ni na voljo, je ni treba vnesti. "
"Za mape &Samba; &eg; ni potreben vnos <guilabel>Vrata</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name:"
msgstr "Ime:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where you give a name to the network connection. It is limited only "
"by your imagination (or alphabet)."
msgstr ""
"Tu omrežni povezavi dodelite ime. Mejo za ime postavlja le vaša domišljija "
"(ali abeceda)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "User:"
msgstr "Uporabnik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the username that will be used to establish the connection."
msgstr "To je uporabniško ime, ki bo uporabljeno za vzpostavitev povezave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Server:"
msgstr "Strežnik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the address of the server you are attempting to add. It can be an IP "
"address or domain name."
msgstr ""
"To je naslov strežnika, ki ga želite dodati. To je lahko naslov IP ali ime "
"domene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port:"
msgstr "Vrata:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you enter the port number you wish to connect to. The defaults are "
"usually sufficient."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesite številko vrat, s katerimi se želite povezati. Privzete "
"nastavitve običajno zadostujejo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not available for &Microsoft; &Windows; (&Samba;) folders."
msgstr "Ni na voljo za mape &Microsoft; &Windows; (&Samba;)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder:"
msgstr "Mapa:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "The path to the folder you wish to connect to should go here."
msgstr "Tu je treba navesti pot do mape, s katero se želite povezati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding:"
msgstr "Kodiranje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the items in this list box to select an encoding for &FTP; and ssh "
"connections."
msgstr ""
"Z elementi v tem seznamu lahko izberete kodiranje za povezave &FTP; in ssh."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create an icon for this remote folder"
msgstr "Ustvarite ikono za to oddaljeno mapo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked an icon will be created allowing access through the "
"remote:/ virtual folder. If it is not checked, a connection will be possible "
"but it will not be accessible from remote:/."
msgstr ""
"Če je to polje označeno, se ustvari ikona, ki omogoča dostop prek "
"oddaljene:/ virtualne mape. Če ni označena, bo povezava mogoča, vendar ne bo "
"dostopna iz oddaljenega:/."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Recent connection:</guilabel> option allows you to re-connect "
"to the last network mount point you connected to using the wizard whether an "
"icon is created or not."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Nedavna povezava:</guilabel> vam omogoča ponovno povezavo "
"z zadnjo omrežno priključno točko, s katero ste se povezali s čarovnikom, ne "
"glede na to, ali je ikona ustvarjena ali ne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use encryption"
msgstr "Uporaba šifriranja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked the ability to make a secure connection will be enabled."
msgstr "Če je označeno, bo omogočena možnost vzpostavitve varne povezave."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available only for WebDav folders."
msgstr "Na voljo samo za mape WebDav."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "&knetattach; Walkthrough"
msgstr "&knetattach; Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will be a quick walkthrough of the Network Folder Wizard. Don't blink "
"or you might miss it."
msgstr ""
"To bo hiter pregled čarovnika za omrežno mapo. Ne pomežikni, sicer ga lahko "
"zamudiš."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below you see the main window of the Network Folder Wizard. It is here that "
"we choose what type of folder we want to add or connect to. For the purposes "
"of this walkthrough we will be using &FTP;. It contains most of the options "
"you will encounter while using the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Spodaj je prikazano glavno okno čarovnika za omrežno mapo. Tu izberemo, "
"katero vrsto mape želimo dodati ali povezati z njo. V tem priročniku bomo "
"uporabljali &FTP;. Vsebuje večino možnosti, s katerimi se boste srečali med "
"uporabo čarovnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the &knetattach; main window"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &knetattach; glavnega okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OK, so we (as in me) have chosen to add an &FTP; folder. Below you see an "
"example of the type of information you will need to add for your particular "
"&FTP; server. After filling it in we press <guibutton>Save &amp; Connect</"
"guibutton> and wait for the magic. Oh yes, if your server requires "
"validation of some kind you will be prompted at this point before being "
"allowed to connect."
msgstr ""
"V redu, torej smo se (jaz) odločili dodati mapo &FTP;. Spodaj je prikazan "
"primer vrste informacij, ki jih morate dodati za svoj strežnik &FTP;. Ko ga "
"izpolnimo, pritisnemo <guibutton>Shrani &amp; Poveži</guibutton> in počakamo "
"na čarovnijo. Če vaš strežnik zahteva kakršno koli potrditev, boste na tej "
"točki pozvani, preden vam bo omogočena povezava."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot showing addition of &FTP; Folder using &knetattach;"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona prikazuje dodajanje &FTP; Mape z uporabo &knetattach;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So now we are all connected now and able to navigate our newly added share. "
"Joy!"
msgstr ""
"Tako smo zdaj vsi povezani in lahko krmarimo po novo dodanem deležu. Radost!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the connected &FTP; folder"
msgstr "Screenshot of the linked &FTP; folder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get back to our network folders all that is necessary is typing "
"<action>remote:/</action> in the location bar of &konqueror; or &dolphin; or "
"select <guilabel>Network</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Za vrnitev v naše omrežne mape je vse, kar potrebujete, vtipkati "
"<action>remote:/</action> v lokacijsko vrstico &konqueror; ali &dolphin; ali "
"izberite <guilabel>Omrežje</guilabel> na plošči <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the remote:/ virtual folder with the added connection"
msgstr "Zaslonska slika oddaljene:/ virtualne mape z dodano povezavo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can even add new folders from the same location by using the "
"<guilabel>Add a Network Folder</guilabel> link. Well that brings us to the "
"end of our walkthrough (told you it would be quick). I wish you the best of "
"luck in your own network folder adventures ;-)"
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo povezave <guilabel>Dodaj omrežno mapo</guilabel> lahko z istega "
"mesta dodate tudi nove mape. S tem smo končali naš sprehod (rekel sem vam, "
"da bo hiter). Želim vam veliko sreče pri vaših pustolovščinah z omrežnimi "
"mapami ;-)"

